            <div class="article_col-main article_col-main-left article_main">
              <div class="article-body" itemprop="articleBody">
                    <p> Below is a rush transcript of MSNBC and Telemundo's Hillary Clinton and Bernie Sanders Town Hall moderated by José Díaz-Balart and Chuck Todd live from Las Vegas on Thursday, Feb. 18 from 9-11 p.m. ET / 6-8 p.m. PT. </p>
                
              
              
              
                    <p> Find full coverage of the race for the White House at <a href="http://www.nbcnews.com/politics/2016-election">Decision 2016</a>. </p>
                
              
              
              
                    <p> <strong>Mandatory credit: &quot;MSNBC and Telemundo&quot;</strong> </p>
                
              
              
              
                    <p> RACHEL MADDOW: The Democratic forum in Las Vegas, two days ahead of the Democratic Caucuses in Nevada, starts right now. </p>
                
              
              
              
                    <p> ... </p>
                
              
