                    <p>   </p>
                
              
              
              
                    <p> We went around the country. We made it clear we would never let that happen. And you know what, their whole plan was, their plan was to give the Social Security trust fund to Wall Street. Imagine that.  </p>
                
              
              
              
                    <p>   </p>
                
              
              
              
